Cricket Analysis Project
🔹 Project Title

Number of Matches Played by Teams (IPL Analysis)

🔹 Description

This project analyzes the number of matches played by different IPL teams using data visualization. A horizontal bar chart is used to clearly compare team participation.

🔹 Visualization Insight

Mumbai Indians played the highest number of matches

Followed by:

Kings XI Punjab

Chennai Super Kings

Royal Challengers Bangalore

Least matches:

Rising Pune Supergiants

Kochi Tuskers Kerala

🔹 Tools Used

Python 🐍

Matplotlib 📊

Pandas

# Step 1: Import libraries
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

# Step 2: Create dataset (IPL Teams & Matches Played)
teams = [
    "Mumbai Indians", "Kings XI Punjab", "Chennai Super Kings",
    "Royal Challengers Bangalore", "Kolkata Knight Riders",
    "Delhi Daredevils", "Rajasthan Royals", "Sunrisers Hyderabad",
    "Deccan Chargers", "Pune Warriors", "Gujarat Lions",
    "Rising Pune Supergiant", "Kochi Tuskers Kerala",
    "Rising Pune Supergiants"
]

matches = [85, 80, 78, 72, 70, 65, 55, 48, 45, 20, 15, 10, 8, 6]

# Step 3: Convert into DataFrame
df = pd.DataFrame({
    "Team": teams,
    "Matches Played": matches
})

# Step 4: Show dataset
print("IPL Dataset:\n")
print(df)

# Step 5: Basic Analysis
print("\nTotal Teams:", df.shape[0])
print("Maximum Matches Played:", df["Matches Played"].max())
print("Minimum Matches Played:", df["Matches Played"].min())

# Step 6: Sort data for better visualization
df_sorted = df.sort_values(by="Matches Played", ascending=True)

# Step 7: Plot Horizontal Bar Chart
plt.figure(figsize=(12, 7))
plt.barh(df_sorted["Team"], df_sorted["Matches Played"])

# Step 8: Add labels and title
plt.xlabel("Number of Matches Played")
plt.ylabel("IPL Teams")
plt.title("Number of Matches Played by IPL Teams")

# Step 9: Add values on bars
for index, value in enumerate(df_sorted["Matches Played"]):
    plt.text(value, index, str(value), va='center')

# Step 10: Adjust layout
plt.tight_layout()

# Step 11: Show graph
plt.show().


## Conclusion
This analysis highlights player consistency and match-winning factors.

